oads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318811" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-2.jpg" alt="Moto e6 plus 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-2-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-2-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318815" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-4.jpg" alt="Moto e6 plus 4" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-4.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-4-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Moto-e6-plus-4-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Jamie Mckane is a guest of Lenovo at IFA 2019 in Berlin, Germany.